<head>
  <meta name="title" content="the Magic Pool (Samwel)"/>
  <meta name="description" content="Samwel is the Cave of the Magic Pools with several standing water pools; Winnemem Wintu medicine men bathed in the pools to gain magic strength (sacred site; the Lost Maiden Olchanolmet tradition)."/>
  <meta name="rights" content="Interpretive: The number, size, and placement of the pools, designating one as THE Magic Pool, its luminous glow and PointLight, and all surrounding lighting and detail. LAYOUT: global_position/level_order/stream_b"/>
